    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ALL_RELEVANT_FLOWS_QUANTIFIED

        public static final CompletenessValues ALL_RELEVANT_FLOWS_QUANTIFIED
        All relevant flows are recorded. [Note: This does not consider yet the quality or representativeness of the data.]

      • RELEVANT_FLOWS_MISSING

        public static final CompletenessValues RELEVANT_FLOWS_MISSING
        One or more relevant flows are not recorded respectively not quantified. [Note: These flows should be found in the Inputs and Outputs with mean amount "0" and marked as "Missing relevant" in the field "Data derivation type/status".]

      • TOPIC_NOT_RELEVANT

        public static final CompletenessValues TOPIC_NOT_RELEVANT
        Process is not relevant for the environmental impact. E.g. it is a dummy process or a generic mixer process, or is not contributing to a specified environmental problem.
